 the interacting mass fraction of the target\nand the projectile in order to translate oblique impacts into equivalent\nhead-on collisions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Jun 2014 22:39:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-06-23"}
