 galaxy merger timescale and the SMBH mass\n- galaxy bulge mass relation dominate the uncertainty in our predictions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Jun 2014 07:45:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 Dec 2014 01:08:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
